### 1. GET all events
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events

### 2. GET published events sorted by startDate
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events?$filter=status eq 'Published'&$orderby=startDate asc

### 3. GET events filtered by type Workshop
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events?$filter=eventType eq 'Workshop'

### 4. GET events with available seats
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events?$filter=registeredCount lt maxAttendees

### 5. GET all registrations for a specific event
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Registrations?$filter=eventId eq 'E01'

### 6. GET speakers sorted by rating descending
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Speakers?$orderby=rating desc

### 7. GET all speakers
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Speakers

### 8. POST a new registration
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Registrations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ID": "R11",
  "eventId": "E01",
  "attendeeName": "Rahul Gupta",
  "attendeeEmail": "rahulg@gmail.com",
  "attendeePhone": "9500000001",
  "company": "SAP",
  "ticketType": "General",
  "registrationDate": "2024-06-15",
  "status": "Confirmed",
  "amountPaid": 2000,
  "paymentId": "PAY011"
}

### 9. PATCH event status from Draft to Published
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events(ID='E03')
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Published"
}

### 10. POST feedback for an event
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Feedback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ID": "F05",
  "eventId": "E01",
  "attendeeEmail": "rohit@gmail.com",
  "overallRating": 5,
  "contentRating": 4,
  "venueRating": 5,
  "speakerRating": 5,
  "comment": "Amazing event loved every session",
  "submittedAt": "2024-07-17T12:00:00"
}

### 11. GET all venues
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Venues

### 12. GET top 3 events
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events?$top=3

### 13. GET events with select fields
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events?$select=ID,title,eventType,status,startDate